text: Bessie Beatrice Carter (born 25 October 1993) is an British actress. She is known for her role as Evie Wilcox on the BBC television series Howards End (2017) and Violet Woodhouse on the ITV television series Beecham House (2019). ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:English television actors Category:Actors from London
title: Bessie Carter
